query:
INSERT INTO committee_sessions (
            number,
            election_id,
            location,
            start_date_time,
            number_of_voters
        ) VALUES (?, ?, "", NULL, ?)
        RETURNING
            id as "id: u32",
            number as "number: u32",
            election_id as "election_id: u32",
            status as "status: _",
            location,
            start_date_time as "start_date_time: _",
            number_of_voters as "number_of_voters: u32"
